Package: archiver
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Archive files for members of a specified Linux group
 Moves files from user home directories to a configurable archive folder,
 preserving the original directory structure. Supports exclude patterns,
 dry-run mode, concurrent-run locking, and JSON reporting.
